      public void loadFacultyFromFile​(java.lang.String fileName)

    • addFaculty

      public boolean addFaculty​(java.lang.String firstName, java.lang.String lastName, java.lang.String id, java.lang.String email, java.lang.String password, java.lang.String repeatPassword, int maxCourses)
      The addFaculty method supports the functionality for adding a Faculty to the list of faculty. Returns true if the faculty member was successfully added, else returns false.
      Parameters:
      firstName - the first name of the faculty member
      lastName - the last name of the faculty member
      id - the id of the faculty member
      email - the email of the faculty member
      password - the password of the faculty member
      repeatPassword - the password of the faculty member repeated
      maxCourses - the maximum number of courses for the faculty member
      Returns:
      boolean representing whether the faculty member was added
      Throws:
      java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - if the firstName, lastName, id, email, password, repeatedPassword, or maxCourses is invalid

    • removeFaculty

      public boolean removeFaculty​(java.lang.String facultyId)
      The removeFaculty method supports the functionality for removing a Faculty from the list of faculty, given the facultyId. Returns true if the faculty member was successfully removed, else returns false.
      Parameters:
      facultyId - the id of the faculty to remove
      Returns:
      boolean representing whether the faculty member was removed

    • getFacultyDirectory

      public java.lang.String[][] getFacultyDirectory()
      Returns a 2D array, where each row is a Faculty and the columns are the firstName, lastName, and id.
      Returns:
      2D String array of Faculty members firstName, lastName, and id

    • getFacultyById

      public Faculty getFacultyById​(java.lang.String id)
      Returns the Faculty member with the given id. If no Faculty member corresponds to the given id, the method returns null.
      Parameters:
      id - the id of the Faculty member to be returned
      Returns:
      the Faculty member with the given id, or null if none is found
